      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 27 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 27 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：顛頤，拂經，于丘頤，征凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one looking downwards for nourishment, which is contrary to what is proper; or seeking it from the height (above), advance towards which will lead to evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
