      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 27 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 27 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：拂頤，貞凶，十年勿用，无攸利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows one acting contrary to the method of nourishing. However firm he may be, there will be evil. For ten years let him not take any action, (for) it will not be in any way advantageous.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
