      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 27 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 27 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：拂經，居貞吉，不可涉大川。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows one acting contrary to what is regular and proper; but if he abide in firmness, there will be good fortune. He should not, (however, try to) cross the great stream.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
